    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped to level 1 per the MRL 2 requirements matrix. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) was satisfied at all five worst-case operating points.",
